  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Sail with the wind:</h2>The <strong>direction of the wind</strong> dictates the speed of your airship. If u try to go against the wind the ship will slow down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/323cc1fe08cc49e67703fced2bb567c3.poster.avif?t=1711386696\" width=500 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/323cc1fe08cc49e67703fced2bb567c3.webm?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/323cc1fe08cc49e67703fced2bb567c3.mp4?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Sharpen your skills:</h2>Use the <strong>recoil</strong> of your shots and the speed of the wind to evade enemy bullets. Along the way you will find plenty of different threats to challenge your piloting abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/5897479ed93dc6b88ed2a5df49049f99.poster.avif?t=1711386696\" width=500 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/5897479ed93dc6b88ed2a5df49049f99.webm?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/5897479ed93dc6b88ed2a5df49049f99.mp4?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Explore the seven skies:</h2>With each sky comes a new challenge to solve and a new world to explore. Will you be able to survive the journey and reach the Seventh Sky?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/886800c0ef83e1e9ea29fb611fb219d1.poster.avif?t=1711386696\" width=500 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/886800c0ef83e1e9ea29fb611fb219d1.webm?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/886800c0ef83e1e9ea29fb611fb219d1.mp4?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Story</h2>Legends say that there are seven skies above the human world. Six of them are worlds of pure madness, each more dangerous than the previous one. But beyond them, at the end of the Journey there is the Seventh Sky, Paradise, a place containing everything men ever wanted. <br>And every year humans send two sailors on a journey in hopes of reaching it. So far out of countless expeditions none has returned. <br><br>You play as Hawk, a young pilot who embarks on the Journey with her trusted companion, a robot parrot. She aims to find her father, who left in search of Paradise many years prior. To reach her destination Hawk will have to question her beliefs and leave everything from her past behind. But will what awaits in the Seventh Sky justify her sacrifice?",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Sail with the wind:</h2>The <strong>direction of the wind</strong> dictates the speed of your airship. If u try to go against the wind the ship will slow down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/323cc1fe08cc49e67703fced2bb567c3.poster.avif?t=1711386696\" width=500 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/323cc1fe08cc49e67703fced2bb567c3.webm?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/323cc1fe08cc49e67703fced2bb567c3.mp4?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Sharpen your skills:</h2>Use the <strong>recoil</strong> of your shots and the speed of the wind to evade enemy bullets. Along the way you will find plenty of different threats to challenge your piloting abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/5897479ed93dc6b88ed2a5df49049f99.poster.avif?t=1711386696\" width=500 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/5897479ed93dc6b88ed2a5df49049f99.webm?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149490/extras/5897479ed93dc6b88ed2a5df49049f99.mp4?t=1711386696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Explore the seven skies:</h2>With each sky comes a new challenge to solve and a new world to explore. Will you be able to survive the journey and reach the Seventh Sky?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.